ip: show / manipulate routing, network devices, interfaces and tunnels
====================
ip address show					# ip addr
ip link set dev net_card_name down
ip link set dev net_card_name up
ip link show net_card_name




wpa_supplicant
====================
wpa_cli -i<net_card_name> scan_results


